The stakes are high as randomly selected tag teams vie for a chance at $100,000.
This is an event you won't want to miss, with the reunion of one of the greatest tag 
teams in TNA history - Beer Money! See your favorite superstars, including Gunner,
 Chris Sabin, Magnus, Samoa Joe, Bully Ray, Mr. Anderson, Austin Aries, The Wolves,
 Kazarian, Curryman, Ethan Carter III, Eric Young, Abyss and more! Leading up to a 
12-main Gauntlet Match for the ultimate in cold hard cash. And you won't want to miss
 a special Knockouts Elimination Match featuring Gail Kim, Lei'D Tapa and The Alpha Female vs.
 ODB, Madison Rayne and Velvet Sky .
